  m_text: "Luke and Daisy went to the Homecoming Dance together.\nAfter a lot of
    convincing, Daisy eventually got Luke to dance. \nA little.\nHe was terrible.\nDaisy
    didn't mind at all.\n\nBrett Kissinger probably isn't going to die alone.\nHe's
    actually a really good kid.\n\n\nThanks for playing!\n- Davis Marriott & Patrick
    Ian Moss"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
